    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯正在竞选，但过渡团队正在努力工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/trump-harris-on-the-trail-but-transition-teams-are-hard-at-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯的团队都在悄悄筹备他们的候任政府，尽管两位候选人仍然专注于在周二极其接近的选举的最后几天赢得总统大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/trump-harris-on-the-trail-but-transition-teams-are-hard-at-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
